「中国黑客导致印度停电」，「未来记录」自己也承认，由于他们无法进入印度的电力系统，因此无法检查代码的细节，「（电力）系统中断和发现不明恶意软件之间的联系没有得到证实」。 此外，印度官方也澄清「没有证据证明中国黑客曾入侵印度电力系统」。（观察者网）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-18471fd4f818b06d35ac92ff3ab89aaa_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "430 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/447177977"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkIj5mczPlMBwEAMaCDYxNjUxNDM0IMqC94EGMAY4rwJADXIJNDQ3MTc3OTc3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1614751305.2313392", "card_id": "Q_445164512", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 233}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "浪费这么多资源，去挖一个根本不存在的比特币，难道就我一个人很讨厌这东西吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-1e9283a90600bb11e66c4633c40ac636_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "378 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/445164512"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkIj5mczPlMBwEAMaCDYxMjA0MTk2IMfGvIEGMCg42wNADnIJNDQ1MTY0NTEyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1614751305.2316582", "card_id": "Q_66753133", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 75}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "钱锺书和杨绛要是真的很恩爱，为什么会写出《围城》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "作家总是有切身体会，才能创作出好作品。看了《围城》，感觉钱钟书对女生的小心思很了解啊。我个人觉得，钱锺书和杨绛确实比大多数夫妻感情都好，但不至于夸大到神仙眷侣的程度。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-fc4dd19029f8ce6a5e88092e3c014253_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "350 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/66753133"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IkIj5mczPlMBwEAMaCDE4OTI4ODUzIIuak88FMBo4zwNAD3IINjY3NTMxMzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1614751305.2320879", "card_id": "Q_3292993